Usage:
  See ./fll --help

Example Usage:
  1) cp fll.conf ..; edit ../fll.conf
  2) ./fll -c ../fll.conf -b /tmp/fll/ -o /tmp/fll/

Dependencies:
  python (>= 2.5)
  python-apt
  python-configobj
  cdebootstrap | debootstrap
  xorriso
  python-fll
  squashfs-tools
  syslinux

Recommends:
  reprepro (for liveapt functionality and extras (amd64 with efi))

----

after a hard break:
# mount
# umount fll-devpts
# umount fll-proc

repeat as long as mounted fll's remain. then cleanup the build-dir
